\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>557<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>3,204<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2c1bfc17f576d6c5f7d31dc8568743502.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Starsquall Shot<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>5<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDeals water damage to enemies in a line,<br>and inflicts frostbite. Frostbitten foes take extra<br>damage.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/238e26f1fb8055213f344b979afe79322.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Special Delivery<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tGrants nearby allies a one-use shield that nullifies<br>damage less than 20% of the user\'s maximum HP,<br>increases their energy levels by three stages, and<br>activates \\"Gifts Ready,\\" preparing two gifts.<br>While this skill is active, the user can distribute<br>gifts by using their force strike. These gifts grant<br>nearby allies a one-use shield that nullifies<br>damage less than 20% of the user\'s maximum HP,<br>and increase their energy levels by three stages.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Skill Haste +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases skill gauge fill rate by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2eacc0ecdcae8474365161935d0e38232.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Water) Frostbite = User Flame Res +7%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Water:<br>reduces flame damage taken by them by 7%<br>for 15 seconds when they successfully inflict<br>an enemy with frostbite. After activating, this<br>ability will not activate again for 10 seconds.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png\\"><\/span><span>Skill Damage +35%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases attack skill damage by 35%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c0b3ec2bdf2af0f73ef2627b87da47152.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Burn Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to burning by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted burning on them, their strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will<br>not activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1a74512b1be6552f814d492e56318e602.png\\"><\/span><span>Queen of Smiles<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When the combo count is 15 or higher, grants<br>the user\'s standard attacks a 25% chance of<br>inflicting freeze for six seconds, and increases<br>damage to frostbitten enemies by 10%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div>When Dragonyule Nefaria&#39;s mana spiral is unlocked, the description of her Flurry Freezer I ability will be updated as follows:<\/div><div>Before: When the combo count is 15 or higher, grants a 6-second buff that gives standard attacks a 10% chance of inflicting freeze.<\/div><div>After: When the combo count is 15 or higher, grants the user&#39;s standard attacks a 10% chance of inflicting freeze for six seconds.<\/div><div>Please note that the ability will behave exactly as it did before and that only the description itself is being updated.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1608184800,"prev_article_id":"1842","next_article_id":"1840","image_path":"","update_time":1608095996}}}'